<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" size="6" color="#000066">&nbsp;The International School</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" size="6" color="#000066">of Moscow</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div class="gmail_default" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>RE: IMPORTANT Health Notification for ISM Rosinka Families</b><br><div style="text-align: left;"><span style="text-align: right;"><br><div style="text-align: right;">Sunday 26th June 2016</div><div style="text-align: right;"><br></div></span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Dear Parents,&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">I am writing to inform you that a family with two children in our school has a confirmed case of Salmonella. <b><i>Due to the specific circumstances of this case, both the family in question and the hospital where their children have been treated believe that the infection occurred outside of school.<br></i></b><br>However, as a matter of precaution, the following action will be taken in school and is strongly recommended to you at home:<br><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><i style="font-weight: bold;">In school:</i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><ul><li>if any student exhibits the symptoms, parents will be notified immediately and asked to collect their child and take them to the doctor.</li><li>a deep clean of both Rosinka campuses will occur immediately.</li><li>a deep clean of the kitchen area will occur immediately.&nbsp;</li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">(as usual) all students will be encouraged to wash their hands regularly and with care, particularly after using the bathroom and before meal times.</span></li></ul><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><i style="font-weight: bold;">At home:</i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><ul><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><i>if your child exhibits symptoms, please keep them away from school, let us know and seek appropriate medical attention. </i></b>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">in the unlikely event that your child has been in contact with another child who developed the infection, be especially vigilant since Salmonella can be passed from person to person, as well as through food.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">take particular care to ensure that any meat, poultry or eggs that you serve are well-cooked.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">support children to ensure that general hygiene and hand washing is very thorough, particularly after using the bathroom and before meal times.</span></li></ul><u style="font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;"><div><u style="font-size: 12pt;">Information about Salmonella</u></div></u></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Salmonella is usually caused by consuming contaminated food. Symptoms include diarrhoea, stomach cramps and sometimes vomiting and fever. These usually last for four to seven days and most people recover without treatment. However, some people infected get seriously ill and may need hospital care, primarily those who become severely dehydrated owing to the symptoms. Salmonella can be spread from person to person by poor hygiene, by failing to wash your hands properly after going to the toilet, or after handling contaminated food.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">For further details, please see the link below:</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><a href="&#10;http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/salmonella-infection/Pages/Introduction.aspx/"><br></a></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><a href="&#10;http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/salmonella-infection/Pages/Introduction.aspx/">http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/salmonella-infection/Pages/Introduction.aspx/</a></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div><font color="#000000" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">Yours Sincerely,</font><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><br>Raymond Finch<br></span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#000000">ISM Rosinka Head Teacher</font><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The International School of Moscow<br></span><i style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></div></font></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
